\begin_layout Standard
We have that: the equilibrium system boils down to:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left[\begin{array}{cc}
-\frac{\omega_{e}}{\psi}\epsilon_{P}^{b} & -\left(\frac{\omega_{\ell}}{\psi}+\frac{\zeta^{b}}{\epsilon^{B}}\right)\\
